---
import Timeline from "../display/Timeline.astro";
import TimelineItem from "../display/TimelineItem.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Experience</h1>

    <div>
        <Timeline class="timeline-snap-icon timeline-compact timeline-vertical">
            <TimelineItem
                title="Matrix"
                subtitle="Software Developer, Fullstack Developer"
                time="2021"
                end={false}
            >
                <p>
                    In Matrix, I worked on the development of various tools for
                    the company, a Discord's chatbot for the company's service
                    platform, and a internal reminder application.
                </p>
            </TimelineItem>
            <TimelineItem
                title="Replit"
                subtitle="Software Developer, Event Managment, Game Engine development"
                time="March 2022 to December 2022"
            >
                <p>
                    In Replit, I worked on the development of a game engine
                    called Kaboom.js, using JavaScript, where I was the
                    maintainer of the project. I added features, fixed bugs, and
                    improved the documentation website, using Next.js.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I also participed in the Replit Reps program, where I
                    organized different Game Jams and Hackathons.
                </p>
            </TimelineItem>
            <TimelineItem
                title="ConLuc. Corp"
                subtitle="Software Developer, UI/UX"
                time="Sep 2023 to Dec 2023"
                start={false}
            >
                <p>
                    In ConLuc. Corp, I worked on the development and refactoring
                    of the UI/UX of a soccer online game, using Unity3D.
                </p>
            </TimelineItem>
        </Timeline>
    </div>
</section>
